# Daily Pipeline — 9-Phase Architecture

**Entry point:** [scripts/run_daily_pipeline.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/scripts/run_daily_pipeline.py)  
**Orchestrator:** [src/orchestrators/daily_pipeline_orchestrator.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/orchestrators/daily_pipeline_orchestrator.py) → [DailyPipelineOrchestrator](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/orchestrators/daily_pipeline_orchestrator.py#36-637)

---

## CLI Arguments (current)

| Arg | Type | Default | Purpose |
|-----|------|---------|---------|
| `--date` | `YYYY-MM-DD` | Yesterday | Target processing date |
| `--dry-run` | flag | off | Validate only, no DB writes |
| `--force` | flag | off | Re-run even if already completed |
| `--db` | path | [data/market_data.duckdb](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/data/market_data.duckdb) | DuckDB database path |
| `--verbose` | flag | off | DEBUG log level |

**Potential future CLI inputs:** `--tickers` (override universe), `--phases` (run subset), `--start-date`/`--end-date` (backfill range), `--max-workers` (parallelism), `--alert-webhook` (notification endpoint).

---

## Phase Map

### Phase 1 — T1 Ingestion *(PARALLEL, CRITICAL)*
| | |
|---|---|
| **Purpose** | Refresh raw market data from external sources |
| **Input** | `target_date`, cached tickers from `price_data`, active tickers from [screener_members](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/orchestrators/daily_pipeline_orchestrator.py#498-510) |
| **Output** | Updated `price_data`, `fundamentals_cache`, `shares_outstanding`, `macro_data` tables |
| **Classes** | `DataRepository`, `FundamentalEngine` (cache-only), `SharesEngine`, `MacroEngine` |
| **Scripts** | [src/data_engine.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/data_engine.py), [src/fundamental_engine.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/fundamental_engine.py), [src/shares_engine.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/shares_engine.py), [src/macro_engine.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/macro_engine.py) |
| **Acceptable input** | Any valid date; auto-skipped if all tickers already fresh. Could accept `--tickers` list or `--source` (yfinance/FMP) |

---

### Phase 2 — Screener Membership *(CRITICAL)*
| | |
|---|---|
| **Purpose** | Determine which tickers qualify for the active screener universe |
| **Input** | `target_date`, `price_data` |
| **Output** | [screener_members](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/orchestrators/daily_pipeline_orchestrator.py#498-510) table (added/removed/active counts) |
| **Classes** | `ScreenerManager` |
| **Scripts** | [src/managers/screener_manager.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/managers/screener_manager.py) |
| **Acceptable input** | Date + optional `--min-price`, `--min-volume`, `--universe-file` filter overrides |

---

### Phase 3 — T2 Screener Features *(CRITICAL)*
| | |
|---|---|
| **Purpose** | Compute lightweight SQL-based features for screener candidates |
| **Input** | `start_date`, [screener_members](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/orchestrators/daily_pipeline_orchestrator.py#498-510), `price_data` |
| **Output** | `t2_screener_features` table |
| **Classes** | `FeaturePipeline` |
| **Scripts** | [src/feature_pipeline.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/feature_pipeline.py) |
| **Acceptable input** | Date range (`start_date`/`end_date`), ticker subset |

---

### Phase 4 — T2 Regime Scores *(non-critical)*
| | |
|---|---|
| **Purpose** | Compute M03 market regime scores (macro/breadth context) |
| **Input** | `macro_data`, `price_data` (incremental) |
| **Output** | `t2_regime_scores` / M03 table |
| **Classes** | `RegimePipeline` |
| **Scripts** | [src/regime_pipeline.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/regime_pipeline.py) |
| **Acceptable input** | No extra args now; could accept `--regime-lookback` window or `--regime-model` variant |

---

### Phase 5 — daily_features Rebuild *(TRANSACTIONAL, CRITICAL)*
| | |
|---|---|
| **Purpose** | Full rebuild of daily_features table (Phases A–E: base, technical, fundamental, labeling, cross-sectional) |
| **Input** | `price_data`, `fundamentals_cache`, `shares_outstanding`, `t2_regime_scores`, [screener_members](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/orchestrators/daily_pipeline_orchestrator.py#498-510) |
| **Output** | [daily_features](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/orchestrators/daily_pipeline_orchestrator.py#527-557) table (commit on success, rollback on failure) |
| **Classes** | `FeaturePipeline` |
| **Scripts** | [src/feature_pipeline.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/feature_pipeline.py), [src/features.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/features.py), [src/alpha_factors.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/alpha_factors.py), [src/cross_sectional_features.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/cross_sectional_features.py) |
| **Acceptable input** | `--incremental` / `--full-rebuild` toggle, `--skip-phases` (e.g. skip labeling) |

---

### Phase 6 — T3 Lazy Materialization *(non-critical)*
| | |
|---|---|
| **Purpose** | Materialize new SEPA breakout candidates (event-driven, date-bounded) |
| **Input** | [daily_features](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/orchestrators/daily_pipeline_orchestrator.py#527-557), `start_date`, `end_date` |
| **Output** | `t3_breakouts` / SEPA breakout table |
| **Classes** | `FeaturePipeline` |
| **Scripts** | [src/feature_pipeline.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/feature_pipeline.py) |
| **Acceptable input** | `--start-date`/`--end-date` for backfill; `--breakout-threshold` parameter |

---

### Phase 7 — View Refresh *(non-critical)*
| | |
|---|---|
| **Purpose** | Recreate all DuckDB views so downstream queries see latest data |
| **Input** | All materialized tables |
| **Output** | Refreshed SQL views (count returned) |
| **Classes** | `ViewManager` |
| **Scripts** | [src/managers/view_manager.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/managers/view_manager.py) |
| **Acceptable input** | `--views` (subset list); no date dependency |

---

### Phase 8 — Training Cache Refresh *(non-critical)*
| | |
|---|---|
| **Purpose** | Materialize `d2_training_cache` for fast ML model training |
| **Input** | [daily_features](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/orchestrators/daily_pipeline_orchestrator.py#527-557), views |
| **Output** | `d2_training_cache` table (row count returned) |
| **Classes** | `ViewManager` |
| **Scripts** | [src/managers/view_manager.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/managers/view_manager.py) |
| **Acceptable input** | `--cache-start-date` (limit training window), `--label-col` override |

---

### Phase 9 — Monitoring *(always runs)*
| | |
|---|---|
| **Purpose** | Log health metrics and fire alerts on anomalies |
| **Input** | `run_stats` from phases 1–8, `pipeline_runs` table, `PIPELINE_ALERT_THRESHOLDS` config |
| **Output** | Log entries, alert messages; no DB writes |
| **Classes** | `PipelineRunManager` |
| **Scripts** | [src/managers/pipeline_run_manager.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/src/managers/pipeline_run_manager.py), [config.py](file:///c:/Users/Hang/PycharmProjects/quantamental/config.py) |
| **Acceptable input** | `--alert-webhook`, `--alert-email`, `--drought-threshold` override |

---

## Dependency & Criticality Summary

```
Phase 1 (price/fund/shares/macro) ──CRITICAL──▶ Phase 2 (screener)
                                                      │
                                       ┌──────────────┴──────────────┐
                                       ▼                             ▼
                               Phase 3 (T2 features)       Phase 4 (regime scores) [non-crit]
                                       │
                               Phase 5 (daily_features) ──CRITICAL / TRANSACTIONAL
                                       │
                               Phase 6 (T3 breakouts) [non-crit]
                                       │
                               Phase 7 (views) [non-crit]
                                       │
                               Phase 8 (training cache) [non-crit]
                                       │
                               Phase 9 (monitoring) [always]
```
